<h1>epiCJD	</h1>

<p>The epiCJD database was designed to assist physicians, researchers and general population to recognize variability of symptoms of prion diseases which are one of the major puzzles of these diseases. Here, we assembled cases reported at Pubmed database and catalogue epidemiological, clinical and genetic data from all single cases reported. Additionally, epiCJD allowed performing searches based on a several criteria and enabling to overview epidemiological traits of prion diseases. </p>

